Bayern Munich have been crowned Bundesliga champions for the third year in a row . 
  Wolfsburg lost 1-0 at Borussia Monchengladbach on Sunday to keep their title hopes alive . 
  Max Kruse scored a last-minute winner in the Bundesliga on Sunday . 
  Bayern have won the title for the 25th time in their history . 
  Pep Guardiola's side are 15 points clear with four games to play . 
 